nodes.text: People Magazine Collector's Edition: The Secrets of Rogue One

People Magazine Collector's Edition: The Secrets of Rogue One is a collector's edition issue of People Magazine. A standalone issue, it was released on December, 2016, and, as indicated by the title, will cover in full depth the then-upcoming film Rogue One: A Star Wars Story. It will come in two versions: a PDF online edition, and a printed version. The printed version will include as a bonus a pair of VR goggles for the VR app, while both versions will have exclusive photos, interviews with the stars, and behind the scenes material inside.
